### Create Electronics product
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/product
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Test Product",
    "price": 100,
    "category": "Electronics"
}

###

### Create Book product
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/product
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Laravel Book",
    "price": 50,
    "category": "book"
}

###

### Get all products
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/products
Accept: application/json

###

### Get products by category
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/products?category=book
Accept: application/json

###

### GET products by searching the name
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/products?search=book
Accept: application/json

###

